videos.description: RJ Barrett passes to Zion Williamson on the low block, who goes up to finish a contested layup for Duke's first points.
videos.headline: Zion's layup gets Duke on the board

videos.description: Georgia Tech's James Banks III cuts down the lane and rises up for a slam with Zion Williamson defending.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Banks dunks over Zion

videos.description: Tre Jones tosses an alley-oop pass to Zion Williamson and he lays it in.
videos.headline: Jones lobs to Zion for the lay-in

videos.description: Zion Williamson calls for the alley-oop and Cam Reddish delivers the pass for a powerful slam.
videos.headline: Zion jams Reddish's alley-oop pass

videos.description: Georgia Tech steals a Duke pass that leads to a Abdoulaye Gueye dunk, then Evan Cole finishes a layup in transition.
videos.headline: Back-to-back buckets extend Georgia Tech's lead

videos.description: Zion Williamson goes up for a dunk and the ball bounces up and off the backboard before going in to tie Georgia Tech.
videos.headline: Zion gets and-1 dunk to fall

videos.description: Zion Williamson calls for the ball and Cam Reddish finds him for an alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Zion throws down alley-oop from Reddish

videos.description: Tre Jones throws a pass behind his back and RJ Barrett slams it home.
videos.headline: Jones' behind-the-back pass leads to Barrett's dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson scores 22 points and throws down some highlight-reel dunks as Duke survives a solid effort by Georgia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion's 22 points, big-time dunks fuel Duke to win) 2019/1/26 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion's 22 points, big-time dunks fuel Duke to win

videos.description: RJ Barrett finishes with 24 points and 11 rebounds as Duke defeats Georgia Tech 66-53 to earn its third straight win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Barrett’s double-double helps Duke top Georgia Tech) 2019/1/26 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Barrett's double-double helps Duke top Georgia Tech
